# Privacy Policy for One Piece Card Tracker

Last updated: [Current Date]

## Introduction
Welcome to One Piece Card Tracker. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application.

## Information We Collect
We collect the following information:
- Email address (when you sign in with Google)
- Basic profile information from your Google account
- Information about your card collection that you choose to save

## How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
- Authenticate you in the application
- Save and manage your card collection
- Provide personalized features

## Data Storage and Security
- Your data is stored securely using Firebase
- We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties
- We implement security measures to protect your data

## Third-Party Services
We use the following third-party services:
- Google Authentication for sign-in
- Firebase for data storage

## Your Rights
You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Request deletion of your data
- Opt out of communications

## Contact
For any questions about this privacy policy, please contact [Your Email]

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.
